Section: net
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Rich Lane <rlane@bigswitch.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), libnl-3-dev | libnl3-dev, libnl-genl-3-dev | libnl3-dev, libnl-route-3-dev | libnl3-dev, pkg-config, python-tz, libcap-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
